Use these instructions provided by Frackz: 

"For you who have problem with it

here's the deal:

1. Open: Keymaker

2. Open the notepad file: Serials

3. Copy the serial that is at the "bottom"

4. Paste it in keymaker

5. Press: "Activate"

6. Press: "Registrer"


Note: When you do this, make sure Alcohol is closed. When you start up Alcohol after: Activating and Registrering, you don't have to press ok or nothing. It's all done!:P"

And then use your firewall to perm. block alcohol.exe from accessing the internet. The Internet server this thing connects to knows that these are bad serial numbers, but if it can't talk to it, it's all good and alcohol works great. Otherwise, it will show up as unregistered.
